{"tid":413282,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實cosplay啲女食得過，不過只可短炒，不可長揸，食完就好走。","createTime":"2017-09-25T10:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T09:43:48.000Z","uid":149401,"like":154,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2947ca98b11422e85f6088915ecb005ee028e61","tid":413282,"uid":149401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"點解？一字記之曰：帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近有位<del>on9</del>純情嘅巴打第一次出pool，溝着個cosplayer。仲話遲d要同個cosplayer求婚，咁咪中伏囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實cosplayer最大嘅問題唔係雞，而係帽。佢地識化妝會打扮，其實玩得過，不過就真係淫底，好姣好賤易食到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。最大嘅問題係佢地個圈好淫亂，帽事特別多，個個都慣背住自己條仔條女偷食，演技特別好，你以為佢真心中意你？其實已經背住你同第條仔chat緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。爆左獲？咪索性分手囉，當無事發生過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無嘅，妖艷賤貨，露肉露得多，仲點知咩叫廉恥。就算佢而家幾冧你，但個底本身淫，對你耐左都會厭。結婚？cosplay d女咁淫，唔洗等7年之癢，7個月就出黎偷食啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之，玩過cosplay嘅女，唔要得架啦。淫底就係淫底，有幾多個出黎行嘅人可以金盆洗手？有幾多個監躉可以浪子回頭？拿，綠帽唔怕帶，最緊要除得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。趁未踏得深之前，放手啦，大把好女等你揀呀，巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddd84ccf4d5cee5ce413481da4115392e5606e0","tid":413282,"uid":135488,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"有名コスプレイヤー月に一度の危険日中出しオフ会<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\